name: io.jahro.console
description:
Jahro Console is a brand new plugin for Unity 3D. 
It The Jahro strives to provide an amazing development experience by an opportunity to use the console for executing commands in a Unity Project directly or in a build of an app on a target device. 

Specially designed for the mobile app debugging process, Jahro brings all its capabilities with the application version on a mobile device.

Undemanding to resources and light as a feather.
- Non-developers\u2019 oriented UX and UI.
- Flexibility of customization and effortless control.
- Simple access to commands during runtime.
- Easy parameters input for commands.

Please check UserGuide in documentation folder.

Visit jahro.io to find more!
